{"tid":2313480,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟外務理事會將討論「香港國安法」","createTime":"2020-12-05T20:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T22:51:54.000Z","uid":264032,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83d7094c0d1ca0247d40a90c908a9aacd4a091b5","tid":2313480,"uid":264032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:19:43.000Z","msg":"歐盟外務理事會將於下星期一(7/12)檢視「香港國安法」嘅實施情況同埋歐洲理事會早前喺七月反制國安法的成效。<br />\n<br />\n會議後將會喺當地時間14:30(香港時間21:30)舉行記者會，並會喺網上直播。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟官方議程表：  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/12/04/media-advisory-foreign-affairs-council-of-7-december-2020/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2Fmedia-advisory-foreign-affairs-council-of-7-december-2020%2F%23&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=7ec18eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/12/04/media-advisory-foreign-affairs-council-of-7-december-2020/#</a><br />\n<br />\n直播網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.consilium.europa.eu/event/en/24264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.consilium.europa.eu%2Fevent%2Fen%2F24264&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=85635472\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.consilium.europa.eu/event/en/24264</a><br />\n<br />\n早前歐洲理事會反制國安法嘅政策範圍：<br />\n1）asylum, migration, visa and residence policy;<br />\n2）exports of specific sensitive equipment and technologies for end use in Hong Kong;<br />\n3）scholarships and academic exchanges involving Hong Kong students and universities;<br />\n4）support to civil society;<br />\n5）the operation of member states&rsquo; extradition arrangements and other relevant agreements with Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/07/28/hong-kong-council-expresses-grave-concern-over-national-security-law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2Fhong-kong-council-expresses-grave-concern-over-national-security-law%2F&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=224fc413\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/07/28/hong-kong-council-expresses-grave-concern-over-national-security-law/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟外務高級代表Josep Borrell嘅Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/josepborrellf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjosepborrellf&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=cc73dd37\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/josepborrellf</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟-香港關係簡介：<br />\n<a href=\"https://eeas.europa.eu/delegations/hong-kong/519/hong-kong-and-eu_en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feeas.europa.eu%2Fdelegations%2Fhong-kong%2F519%2Fhong-kong-and-eu_en&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=a52e8bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://eeas.europa.eu/delegations/hong-kong/519/hong-kong-and-eu_en</a>"},{"pid":"6980d87f7158ca7cb478f2c3a5cac4b98be7af35","tid":2313480,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"993c75bab3fe8f08aa93ae0cf9a24a15bb0c296c","tid":2313480,"uid":264032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6980d87f7158ca7cb478f2c3a5cac4b98be7af35","tid":2313480,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:23:58.000Z","msg":"歐盟對中國喺外交上做到嘅嘢好有限，特別係香港問題"},{"pid":"e3bae221d87dcfc989204836cf16ee1378a28634","tid":2313480,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:25:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b9bcdfad8e61b291cca25a60368aaf2ce7f69a","tid":2313480,"uid":264032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3bae221d87dcfc989204836cf16ee1378a28634","tid":2313480,"uid